<html lang="ja">
<link>
<meta charset="utf-8" />

<title>リナちゃんボード「どこ？」 | そこんところ工房</title>
<meta name="description" content="二次創作ミニゲームです。「璃奈ちゃん、どこ？」シャッフルされたダンボールから、隠れた璃奈ちゃんを見つけ出そう！">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">

<meta property="og:title" content="リナちゃんボックス「どこ？」" />
<meta property="og:site_name" content="リナちゃんボックス「どこ？」" />
<meta property="og:type" content="game" />
<meta property="og:description" content="「璃奈ちゃん、どこ？」シャッフルされたダンボールから、隠れた璃奈ちゃんを見つけ出そう！" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://games.sokontokoro-factory.net/rinadoko/" />
<meta property="og:image" content="https://games.sokontokoro-factory.net/rinadoko/assets/images/ogp.jpg" />
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">

<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/50ec062835.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/platform/1.3.5/platform.min.js"></script>

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./assets/css/launch-before-guide.css" />
<style>
    @font-face {
        font-family: 'PixelMplus12-Bold';
        src: url(assets/fonts/PixelMplus12-Bold.ttf);
    }

    body {
        margin: 0;
    }

    #app {
        display: flex;
        height: 100vh;
        /* https://zenn.dev/tak_dcxi/articles/2ac77656aa94c2cd40bf */
        height: -webkit-fill-available;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;

        background-image: url("./assets/images/back.png");
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: right 10% bottom 50%;
    }

    .container {
        position: absolute;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .container--hide {
        opacity: 0;
    }

    .title {
        padding-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .title__text {
        font-family: "PixelMplus12-Bold";
        font-size: 40px
    }

    .guide {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .guide__text {
        font-family: "PixelMplus12-Bold";
        font-size: 20px
    }

    .select-guide {
        display: none;
        padding-bottom: 200px;
    }

    .select-guide .select-guide__text {
        font-family: "PixelMplus12-Bold";
        font-size: 20px
    }

    .share-controller {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 50px;
    }

    .share-controller--hide {
        display: none;
    }

    .share-controller .twitter-share {
        background-color: #039be5;
        text-align: center;
        cursor: pointer;

        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .share-controller .twitter-share .twitter-share__icon {
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px
    }

    .share-controller .twitter-share .twitter-share__label {
        color: white;
        font-family: "PixelMplus12-Bold";
        font-size: 20px
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="launch-before-guide" class="launch-before-guide">
    <div class="launch-before-guide__title">
        <div class="app-title__game-name">リナちゃんボックス「どこ？」</div>
        <div class="app-title__author">produced by そこんところ工房</div>
    </div>
    <div id="game-launch-button"
         class="launch-before-guide__button launch-before-guide__button--initializing"></div>
    <div class="launch-before-guide__note">
        <div class="note__label">動作環境について</div>
        <div class="note__body">
            リリース時の最新OS(Android, iOS)、最新ブラウザ(Chrome, Safari)で動作確認をしています。
            TwitterやLineなどのアプリ内ブラウザでは、正常に動作しない恐れがあります。
            その他不明点がありましたら、<a href="<%= helpUrlJa %>">ヘルプページ</a>を確認してください。<br />
        </div>

        <div class="note__label">Operating environment</div>
        <div class="note__body">
            It's tested on latest OS (Android, iOS) and latest browser (Chrome, Safari). It may not work
            properly
            on In-app browser of Twitter, Line and like.<br />
            If you have any question, please check out <a href="<%= helpUrlEn %>">help page</a>.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="launch-before-guide__environment">
        <div class="environment-item">
            <span class="environment-item__label">Application: </span>
            <span class="environment-item__value">v<%= appVersion %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="environment-item">
            <span class="environment-item__label">Device: </span>
            <span class="environment-item__value"><script>document.write(platform.product || "unknown")</script></span>
        </div>
        <div class="environment-item">
            <span class="environment-item__label">OS: </span>
            <span class="environment-item__value">
                <script>document.write(platform.os.family + " v" + platform.os.version)</script>
            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="environment-item">
            <span class="environment-item__label">Browser: </span>
            <span><script>document.write(platform.name + " v" + platform.version)</script></span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="app" style="display: none">
    <div id="title" class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <span class="title__text">リナちゃんボックス「どこ？」</span></div>
        <div class="guide">
            <span class="guide__text">タップしてリナちゃんを見付ける！</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="select-guide" class="container select-guide">
        <span class="select-guide__text">リナちゃんはどこ？</span>
    </div>
    <div id="share-controller" class="share-controller share-controller--hide">
        <div id="twitter-share" class="twitter-share">
            <i class="fab fa-twitter twitter-share__icon"></i>
            <span class="twitter-share__label">Twitterで結果をつぶやく</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <canvas id="pixi"></canvas>
</div>
</body>
</html>
